com.projetloki.genesis.image

Class TextShape.Glyph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.projetloki.genesis.image.Shape
      • com.projetloki.genesis.image.TextShape.Glyph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Hashable
    Enclosing class:
    TextShape

    public static final class TextShape.Glyph
extends Shape
    A single glyph in a text shape. There are two different glyph objects representing the letter B in the text shape "BOB". One is the translate of the other. The union of all the glyphs in a text shape is the text shape itself.

    See TextShape.glyphs() for an example.
